\f2\fs32  is a electrical meter specifically designed to measure very large resistances, particularly the resistance of electric insulation, resistance which is too large to be measured accurately with a DMM. It consists of an internal high voltage source (up to 1000 V), an accurate ammeter, and a display scale marked in megohms.   \
